{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan an Nasai","section":{"13":"The Book of Forgetfulness (In Prayer)"},"section_detail":{"13":{"hadithnumber_first":1179,"hadithnumber_last":1366,"arabicnumber_first":1179,"arabicnumber_last":1366}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1204,"arabicnumber":1204,"text":"Rapporté par Abu Qatadah : Le Messager d’Allah (ﷺ) priait en portant Umamah. Quand il se prosternait, il la posait, et quand il se relevait, il la reprenait dans ses bras","grades":[{"name":"Abu Ghuddah","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":13,"hadith":26}}]}